{"id":329816547,"lang":"cpp","time":"1 year, 8 months","timestamp":1587809631,"status_display":"Accepted","runtime":"4 ms","url":"/submissions/detail/329816547/","is_pending":"Not Pending","title":"Find the Minimum Number of Fibonacci Numbers Whose Sum Is K","memory":"6.7 MB","code":"class Solution {\n    #define LL long long int \npublic:\n    int findMinFibonacciNumbers(int k) {\n        vector<LL> all = {1,1};\n        \n        LL a  = 1,b = 1,c;\n        while(c < 1.1e9 ){\n            c = a+b;\n            a = b;\n            b = c;\n            all.push_back(c);\n        }\n        int ans = 0;\n        reverse(all.begin(),all.end());\n        \n        for(int c : all){\n            if(k == 0) break;\n            if(k-c >=0){\n                ++ans;\n                k-=c;\n            }\n        }\n        return ans;\n        \n    }\n};","compare_result":"","title_slug":"find-the-minimum-number-of-fibonacci-numbers-whose-sum-is-k"}
